Sentence (Powell), 


                     Nine months' hard labour; 


                     sentence on Waite was postponed to next Sessions.




Goldstein was released on Mr. Wolzer's recognisances in ₤50 and his own in ₤10 to come up for judgment if called upon; 


Jordan was sentenced to eight months' imprisonment; 


Evansky to six months' imprisonment.

Verdict (each prisoner), 

                     Not guilty of murder; 

                     Guilty of attempted murder, with a very strong recommendation to mercy.
